'From Squeak3.7alpha of ''11 September 2003'' [latest update: #5657] on 9 February 2004 at 11:18:06 am'!"Change Set:		indentClipText-bfDate:			9 February 2004Author:			Bert FreudenbergWhen copying the text of an indented list via the red halo menu, the individual items where not indented, making the result illegible. Fixed."!!IndentingListItemMorph methodsFor: 'accessing' stamp: 'bf 2/9/2004 10:55'!userString	"Add leading tabs to my userString"	^ (String new: indentLevel withAll: Character tab), super userString! !